{"tid":829669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青山國師：思覺失調是什麼？","createTime":"2018-09-20T15:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T18:13:57.000Z","uid":72280,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea69da2c21036d3463e9c64bc21602227bc5b7db","tid":829669,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051011_37be292294fd36e24025999d500d9601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051011_37be292294fd36e24025999d500d9601.jpg&h=a752a82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「思覺失調」是指一種早期不正常的精神狀態，一般會有妄想、幻覺、思想及言語紊亂等情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/09/07/25844_20160907120654_57cf925eabb1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F09%2F07%2F25844_20160907120654_57cf925eabb1d.gif&h=38a800b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當一個人出現「思覺失調」時，他的思維、情感、感覺會脫離現實。任何年齡人士都有機會患上「思覺失調」，如能及早察覺和得到適切的治療，是可以減低「思覺失調」所帶來的傷害和避免誘發更嚴重的精神病。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051252_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051252_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=53b766ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n情況就如「發燒」一樣，「發燒」是疾病前期的一個徵狀，若果我們不加理會或掉以輕心，便有可能演變成嚴重的疾病如肺炎等，因此我們應認真處理「思覺失調」這個狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">思覺失調的病徵</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051359_4d5b85fa4d8cfc4ec96c5e427b1cef34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051359_4d5b85fa4d8cfc4ec96c5e427b1cef34.jpg&h=8f631d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>思想及言語紊亂 </strong><br />\n談話內容貧乏、說話急迫、缺乏主題、雜亂無章、語無倫次，以至別人難以明白理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051515_75885837e367f72670232d785e371a96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051515_75885837e367f72670232d785e371a96.jpg&h=763bb201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>妄想</strong> <br />\n一種脫離現實或令人難以置信的想法，但出現「思覺失調」的人則深信不疑。例如他們會有被監視及被迫害的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051758_304447c10b27dd2b280d7fdfe429e08c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051758_304447c10b27dd2b280d7fdfe429e08c.jpg&h=8b4d9e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>幻覺</strong><br />\n出現「思覺失調」的人會看到、聽到、感覺到一些其他在場人士無法感受到的聲音或事物，但對他們來說是一種非常真實的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/052133_a080a87586b0198b68078fd4194074cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F052133_a080a87586b0198b68078fd4194074cd.jpg&h=2ec5352a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>其他與「思覺失調」相關的表徵</strong><br />\n懶顧儀容、蓬頭垢面；自我隔離、不願接觸別人；缺乏求學或工作的動力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051915_3cc83a2e872550837dd75db4a932d323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051915_3cc83a2e872550837dd75db4a932d323.jpg&h=a44a4b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救救病人，課金治療連結：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise&amp;host=%E9%99%B3%E9%9B%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise%26host%3D%25E9%2599%25B3%25E9%259B%25B2&d=VUUc2fuwnPA%2FjAcv7wt5ZuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=ae32df21\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise&amp;host=%E9%99%B3%E9%9B%B2</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"964cc0dc17a785ac889ce38c2b0428c82f0c47ca","tid":829669,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:29:30.000Z","msg":"原文：[圖文並荗] 陳雲：思覺失調是甚麼？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/283024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/283024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3aeb7b3b66b54b07b29827825bfb54f128a77f1f","tid":829669,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"其實陳老師好正常既<br />\n<br />\n睇女時會射精"},{"pid":"86d6344349f0188590c6b00cd6c7dcd76aa76d3e","tid":829669,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aeb7b3b66b54b07b29827825bfb54f128a77f1f","tid":829669,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"其實陳老師好正常既<br />\n<br />\n睇女時會射精"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:13:57.000Z","msg":"咁做愛時昵？"}]}